name: Crosshatch Men's Windcheater Jacket - Black
meta_title: Crosshatch Men's Windcheater Jacket - Black At New Fashion
meta_description: Crosshatch Men's Windcheater Jacket - Black At New Fashion. This black windcheater is made from shower proof material and features funnel neckline.
description:
Men's windcheater jacket by Crosshatch.

This black windcheater is made from shower proof material and features funnel neckline.

  • Crosshatch jacket
  • Funnel neckline
  • Shower proof
  • 2 front side pockets
  • 1 front chest pocket with zip and Crosshatch Black Label printing
  • Multiple zip placket trought front
  • Ribbed inner collar for added warmth 
  • Ribbed inner cuffs
  • Fleece lined
  • Large Crosshatch print on back neckline

 

About Crosshatch:

It was the year 2000, the turn of the millennium, when the City of Manchester became known as the fashion capital of the UK, one of the biggest contributors to this achievement was the fashion brand Crosshatch.

Crosshatch was inspired by the success of the city of Manchester, which is known for its music culture with iconic bands such as Oasis, Chemical Brothers and also for its passion of football with the world renowned red of United and blue of City.
short_description:
This black windcheater is made from shower proof material and features funnel neckline. Fleece lining, ribbed inner cuffs and neckline for added warmth.

About Crosshatch:

It was the year 2000, the turn of the millennium, when the City of Manchester became known as the fashion capital of the UK, one of the biggest contributors to this achievement was the fashion brand Crosshatch.

Crosshatch was inspired by the success of the city of Manchester, which is known for its music culture with iconic bands such as Oasis, Chemical Brothers and also for its passion of football with the world renowned red of United and blue of City.

description:
Vīriešu vējjaka no Crosshatch.

Šī melnā vīriešu jaka ir izgatavota no lietus necaurlaidīga materiāla un oderēta ar vilnu.

  • Crosshatch vīriešu jaka
  • Augsta apkakle

Par Crosshatch:

Tas bija 2000, tūkstošgades pagrieziens, kad Mančestera kļuva pazīstama kā modes galvaspilsēta Lielbritānijā, viens no lielākajiem šī panākuma iemesliem bija modes brends Crosshatch.

Crosshatch iedvesmojās no Mančesteras pilsētas panākumiem, kura ir pazīstama ar savu mūzikas kultūru un ikoniskām mūzikas grupām - Oasis un Chemical Brothers.

About Crosshatch:

It was the year 2000, the turn of the millennium, when the City of Manchester became known as the fashion capital of the UK, one of the biggest contributors to this achievement was the fashion brand Crosshatch.

Crosshatch was inspired by the success of the city of Manchester, which is known for its music culture with iconic bands such as Oasis, Chemical Brothers and also for its passion of football with the world renowned red of United and blue of City.
